    • _setNextValue

      public void _setNextValue(Integer value)
      Description copied from class: AbstractReadChannel
      Sets the next value. Internal method. Do not call directly.

      If the Unit of the Channel is cumulated and 'value' is null, it is silently ignored. Cumulated values must be steadily increasing and should never get reset to null. See Unit.
